<p><a href="https://matrix.to/#/@cogitri:cogitri.dev">Cogitri</a> announces</p>
<blockquote>
<p>GSoC intern Visvesh <a href="https://gitlab.gnome.org/Cogitri/Health/-/merge_requests/118">added support in Health</a> for sending the user notifications to remind them that they haven&rsquo;t met their daily step goal yet.</p>
</blockquote>


